{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 6632612}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 3.421, de 29 de noviembre de 2007, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, autor&#xED;zase a INVERTEC OSTIMAR S.A. para instalar, por el per&#xED;odo de seis meses contados desde la fecha de la presente resoluci&#xF3;n, colectores de semillas de mit&#xED;lidos en tres sectores ubicados en Bah&#xED;a de Tongoy, IV Regi&#xF3;n, cada uno con una superficie de 1,97 hect&#xE1;reas, cuyas coordenadas geogr&#xE1;ficas, referidas a la carta SHOA N&#xBA; 4113 Datum, PSAD 69, son:</div><br><div class=\"p\">Sector 1</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; V&#xE9;rtice&nbsp; &nbsp;  Latitud (S)&nbsp; &nbsp;  Longitud (W)</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  A&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;24,00&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;07,00&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  B&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;24,00&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;01,00&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  C&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;28,00&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;01,00&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  D&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;28,00&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;07,00&quot;</div><br><div class=\"p\">Sector 2</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; V&#xE9;rtice&nbsp; &nbsp;  Latitud (S)&nbsp; &nbsp;  Longitud (W)</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  A&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;28,40&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;07,00&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  B&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;28,40&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;01,00&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  C&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;32,40&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;01,00&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  D&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30&#xB0;17&apos;32,40&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp;  71&#xB0;34&apos;07,00&quot;</div><br><div class=\"p\">Sector 3</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; V&#xE9;rtice&n